<span id="freeTextContainer2964994305318201082">I wish more modern fantasy books were like this. Hints a flirtation but no full on romances. Great story line. Great characters with room to grow as the series progresses. The end left me with a lot of questions I really hope another book is in the works to answer. I literally went &quot;WHAT?! IT&apos;S OVER ALREADY!? NOOOOOO!&quot;<br/>Narrator in the audio edition was perfect for this story. Kept me invested in the story without putting too much effort into creating character voices. Yes, there were slight diffe</span>
  <span id="freeText2964994305318201082" style="display:none">I wish more modern fantasy books were like this. Hints a flirtation but no full on romances. Great story line. Great characters with room to grow as the series progresses. The end left me with a lot of questions I really hope another book is in the works to answer. I literally went "WHAT?! IT'S OVER ALREADY!? NOOOOOO!"<br />Narrator in the audio edition was perfect for this story. Kept me invested in the story without putting too much effort into creating character voices. Yes, there were slight difference to how the characters sounded but I feel that came more from the author's ability to write their dialog rather than the narrator creating a voice for them.<br />Great mid level book and above, says a 33 year old.</span>
