  <span id="freeText7009183077057462929" style="display:none">One word.....amazing!!<br />I enjoy middle grade books and this is one of my favourites. It has everything I like, journeys between worlds, magical objects, dragons, witches and an unexpected plot twist. <br /><br />English is my second language, but the book catches me, it is so incredibly narrated and written that I read it as if it were written in my language. <br /><br />The world is so beautifully constructed that I could really appreciate every detail and feel within story.<br /><br />I love every character, but I am more fond of Archibald. I love his heart, curious and clever but at the same time so noble and pure that he could see beyond just dragons.</span>
